ALLO 5.1 Reported bug fixes and performance improvements

Integrated workspace improvements: An improved cockpit view consolidates all your frequently used work apps in one place and makes them easier to manage. Improved OKR tracking: Setting and tracking goals is easier than ever. Check out the new OKR features that provide a more intuitive user experience. Project Management Updates: Experience better collaboration with newly updated task assignment and milestone tracking features. Whiteboard Features: New features have been added for working with canvas! Express and visualize your ideas more creatively. Bug fixes and performance improvements: Bug fixes and performance optimizations have been made for a better user experience. If you are curious about ALLO please let us know at sales allo.io!

ALLO 4.9 Video conferencing has become even more comfortable! Both sound and picture quality have been improved allowing you to conduct video conferences more comfortably! Don t worry about conducting a video conference with a large number of people on a small screen. Now you can scroll left and right. Please come and say hello to all the participants! Don t worry about privacy! You can now turn off my screen during video conferences. We also caught hidden bugs. If you find any other bugs please feel free to contact our customer center.
